      EASY SETUP<br>& USAGE
    </p>
    <p style="padding: 0 20px; font-size: 22px; line-height: 28px; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">
      Simple to install, even easier to use. Make content updates in minutes.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Feature: Seamless Integration -->
  <div style="text-align: center; flex: 1; min-width: 220px; padding: 10px;">
    <%= image_tag 'integration.jpg', alt: 'seamless integration', style: "width: 180px; display: inline;" %>
    <p style="font-size: 28px; color: #6A5ACD; letter-spacing: 1px; text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px #87CEEB; font-weight: 600;">
